{"tid":2418784,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國財政部長Yellen再批比特幣：效率極差的交易方式 投資者恐蒙受相關潛在損失","createTime":"2021-02-23T01:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T02:40:14.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b11a53d62563ea15d49f32427ee5f62eaab81f67","tid":2418784,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T01:36:31.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國財政部長葉倫（Janet Yellen）週一（22日）再對比特幣發出警告，指該加密貨幣不僅效率極差，也對投資者及大眾構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n《CNBC》報導，儘管比特幣本週價格開始回落，但仍受到各方推動，維持再5.3萬美元上方交易。但葉倫警告，關於比特幣的合理性及穩定性存有重大疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她反而擔心比特幣更常被用於非法融資，「這是1種效率極低的交易方式，處理這些交易所消耗的能量非常驚人。」<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n葉倫表示：「這個1種高度投機性的資產，人們應該警覺到它可能極具波動性，而我擔心投資者恐蒙受相關的潛在損失。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3446392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3446392&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=e68a22f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3446392&h=255bd4fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3446392</a>"},{"pid":"d1d2b4b00f24e5401f095f1b4297147d38a25e84","tid":2418784,"uid":196625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T01:40:01.000Z","msg":"八婆"},{"pid":"e7b371b0ecdc353d80f71603825722f90997d8b0","tid":2418784,"uid":91606,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T01:43:03.000Z","msg":"fiat is scam<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8711dd7afaadcc799dbee02962b2174a9c309e","tid":2418784,"uid":336429,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b11a53d62563ea15d49f32427ee5f62eaab81f67","tid":2418784,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T01:36:31.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國財政部長葉倫（Janet Yellen）週一（22日）再對比特幣發出警告，指該加密貨幣不僅效率極差，也對投資者及大眾構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n《CNBC》報導，儘管比特幣本週價格開始回落，但仍受到各方推